蟬<br />\n鋼鍊FA<br />\n未聞花名<br />\n翼之奇幻旅程，xxxholic<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">漫畫版</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Alive最終進化少年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n呢排重睇緊翼之奇幻旅程動畫<br />\n準備睇埋xxxholic<br />\n漫畫同動畫分別好大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n翼同holic動畫好似爛尾<br />\n出動畫嗰陣漫畫根本未完，動畫組求尻其寫<br />\n不過老實講，我話爛係因為佢冇還原返clamp既世界觀<br />\n你當獨立作品又唔算好差既，制作當時黎講係好既<br />\n同埋始終clamp種畫風好靚好有特色<br />\n睇你當睇故事定係clamp<br />\n其實翼同holic成個故事要睇兩三次先明<br />\n但漫畫真係寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇唔明下有劇透</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">holic主角其實係代替真小狼既存在，因為真小狼要穿越搵真小櫻，但一個時空原本有既人唔可以無故消失，而真小狼正係假櫻狼故事後期穿越去日本生既，同時兩個故事時間流動唔同，所以後來四月一日好獨咁生存左幾百年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但狼黑鋼法伊都只係過左幾年繼續穿越</span></span><br />\nholic同翼都有出第二集<br />\n翼次元記仲有xxxholic 戻<br />\n懷疑clamp班大嬸冇貨賣仲推埋百變小櫻上中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有得睇都係繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> shut up and take my money"},{"pid":"cc958985a83d88f55efa98d3c91c1505f295f100","tid":309013,"uid":107844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>四月是你的謊言<br />\n啱啱翻睇完</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜冇人覺得似韓劇？我最初睇漫畫已經估到哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左歌好聽，根本動畫版韓劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdda40cc7ba65b9943497f4f13603a175f31316","tid":309013,"uid":79918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl